data.description: Great 2/1 with almost 1/3 acre lot.  New 18x23 building installed with roll up doors for hobby enthusiasts or car mechanics.  Home and extra building are fenced but property extends further than that which is fenced.  New vinyl flooring in living area and some fresh paint inside.  Gas stove for the cooks along with granite countertops.  Plenty of room to add a prep island if desired.  Roof is newer, HWH is newer, as well as HVAC.  Really nothing to do here except put your personal touches on it.
